# Browser Open (`touch-browser-open`)

## When to Use
- Open URLs quickly with default or specific browsers.

## Trigger
- Feature ID: `browser.open`
- Commands: `url / link / open / 浏览器 / 网页`

## Core Capabilities
- 浏览器打开：默认浏览器与指定浏览器快速打开链接
- Supported platforms: `win32, darwin`

## Config & Data
- Config/data files: `recent-browsers.json`
- Plugin directory: `plugins/touch-browser-open`

## Permissions
- Required: `system.shell`; Optional: `clipboard.write`

## Quick Start
1. In CoreBox, type `url`.
2. Press Enter on the action you need.
3. Grant permissions when prompted.
